1. Tóm tắt¶

i dch covid-19 xut hin t cui nm 2019, cho n nay n lan rng ra hu ht cc quc gia v vng lnh th trn th gii, gy thit hi nghim trng v mi mt v kinh t, x hi....

Mc d c vaccine phng nga covid-19 nhng dch bnh ny vn cn honh honh nhiu quc gia, lin tc xut hin cc bin th mi nguy him.

V th, nhm chn tp d liu lin quan n vn ny phn tch tnh hnh dch bnh covid-19.

Nhm t ra mt s cu hi nghin cu v dch Covid-19, nh gi xem i dch ny c ph thuc vo cc yu t nh nn kinh t, dn s hay khng? Tnh hnh dch bnh nh th no khi bin th Omicron xut hin? Hn na, nhm cng mun nh gi xem liu vic tim vaccine c lm gim bt s ca mc, s ca t vong hay lm gim i t l t vong ca Covid-19 hay khng ?

Link github cha th mc data: https://github.com/NMS1010/P4DA_Final_Project

Gii thch cc bin s dng

Bin M t
continent Tn chu lc
location Tn nc
date Ngy quan st
total_cases Tng s ca mc covid 19 c xc nhn
new_cases S ca mc mi covid 19 theo ngy c xc nhn
total_deaths Tng s ca covid 19 t vong c xc nhn
new_deaths S ca covid 19 t vong mi theo ngy c xc nhn
total_vaccinations Tng s liu vaccine
people_vaccinated Tng s ngi tim t nht mt mi vaccine
people_fully_vaccinated Tng s ngi tim liu vaccine theo quy nh
population Tng dn s

Qua biu  Boxplot ta thy min gi tr ca t l t vong do dch bnh, cng vi t l t vong trung bnh ca nhm nc c nn kinh t ang pht trin ln hn cc nc pht trin

Thc hin kim nh thng k cho 2 nhm cc quc gia c nn kinh t pht trin v nn kinh t ang pht trin hn

Mi quan h gia hai bin C (Nhm kinh t) --> Q (T l t vong): hai nhm c lp => Ta thc hin T-test

Ta t gi thuyt thng k

H0: t l t vong ti nhm quc gia pht trin v nhm cc quc gia ang pht trin l nh nhau.

Ha: t l t vong ti nhm quc gia pht trin s cao hn so vi cc quc gia ang pht trin.

T biu  ta cng c th thy c rng t l t vong qua cc ngy ca bin th DELTA ln hn OMICRON.

Da vo biu t l t vong ca 2 loi bin th v h s tng quan, nhm em a ra nhn xt:

  • Bin th DELTA c mi tng quan mnh hn so vi bin th OMICRON. (gia 2 bin NewCases v NewDeaths theo tng ngy)
  • Bin th DELTA c tc ly lan nhanh, s ca t vong mi mi ngy tng cao dn n t l t vong cao.
  • Bin th OMICRON c tc ly lan nhanh vt tri so vi bin th DELTA (mc d bin th OMICRON xut hin sau) nhng v s ca t vong mi mi ngy th bin th OMICRON t hn dn ti t l t vong cng thp hn bin th DELTA

c th a ra kt lun chc chn, ta thc hin kim nh thng k T-test trn 2 nhm c lp: t l t vong v dch bnh mi ngy ca hai nhm bin th DELTA v OMICRON

Ta t gi thuyt:

H0: t l t vong ca hai nhm bin th l nh nhau

Ha: t l t vong ca bin th DELTA cao hn OMICRON.

In [160]:

Ta c p_value = 1.8819579900609447e-83 < 0,05 v t = 24.09083434337719 > 0 => Ta bc b gi thuyt H0, chp nhn Ha

Nhn xt:

Ta c th a ra kt lun rng t l t vong ca nhm bin th DELTA cao hn OMICRON.

Do c th ni tuy bin th OMICRON lm gia tng nhanh chng s ca mc nhng t l t vng li thp hn so vi bin th DELTA. Vy bin th OMICRON c th t gy nguy him hn DELTA nhng s ca mc tng nhanh c th lm qu ti h thng y t mt s quc gia.

Chng ta khng nn xem thng bt k loi bin th no ca Covid-19

4. Kết luận¶

Kt qu nhm t c

  1. Tnh hnh dch bnh cc nc u c th nguy him nh nhau, khng phn bit dn s, nn kinh t ca cc quc gia
  2. Vaccine ng gp vai tr to ln trong vic y li dch bnh Covid-19, nh s xut hin ca n m tnh hnh dch ang c kim sot. Tuy s ca mc mi mi ngy vn tng nhng t l t vong gim ng k so vi trc khi c vaccine
  3. Bin chng OMICRON xut hin gn y khin cho s ca mc tng nhanh t bin, lm qu ti h thng y t ca nhiu nc trn th gii. Tuy nhin, so vi bin chng DELTA th t l t vong ca bin chng OMICRON thp hn, c l cng nh s xut hin ca vaccine. iu lm cho th gii dn kim sot c i dch, tin ti bnh thng ho mi th.
